  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765203279\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.poster.avif?t=1765203279\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.webm?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.mp4?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Terminal squad: swarmites is a game with indirect control where you must erect a chain of buildings, which generate resources for construction or the combat units for destruction of an enemy. The key to the victory is a smart sequence of actions and keeping of a balance between the erection of combat, defensive and manufacturing facilities.<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A base as a single entity<br></li><li>Fight against an infinite flow of enemies through erection of a chain of buildings<br></li><li>Random level modifiers strengthen your enemy<br></li><li>Use the skills and the explorations in the proper moment in order to gain a tactical superiority<br></li><li>Adjust an energy flow to the buildings through their connection and disconnection in order to increase or decrease the rate of production or defence at a certain part of chain.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.poster.avif?t=1765203279\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.webm?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1217330/extras/cb1efa5cfd7f8035f47b5f8e79a91e3d.mp4?t=1765203279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Terminal squad: swarmites is a game with indirect control where you must erect a chain of buildings, which generate resources for construction or the combat units for destruction of an enemy. The key to the victory is a smart sequence of actions and keeping of a balance between the erection of combat, defensive and manufacturing facilities.<br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A base as a single entity<br></li><li>Fight against an infinite flow of enemies through erection of a chain of buildings<br></li><li>Random level modifiers strengthen your enemy<br></li><li>Use the skills and the explorations in the proper moment in order to gain a tactical superiority<br></li><li>Adjust an energy flow to the buildings through their connection and disconnection in order to increase or decrease the rate of production or defence at a certain part of chain.</li></ul>",
